<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your OTP Code</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h1 style="color: #2196F3;">Your OTP Code</h1>
    <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) is:</p>
    <div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: 5px; margin: 0; color: #2196F3;">{{otp}}</h2>
    </div>
    <p>This code will expire in {{expiryTime}}.</p>
    <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px;">Never share this code with anyone.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>